OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FITV is 70 years old this year and, in
OL,7,Fsome ways, it is looking its age.
OL,9,FThe company still has the ability to
OL,10,Freach a mass audience, but its share
OL,11,Fprice - which jumped this morning -
OL,12,Ftells you the market view: ITV's
OL,13,Ffuture as a standalone, independent
OL,14,Fbroadcaster is not the brightest.
OL,16,FEnter Sky - the UK's biggest pay-TV
OL,17,Fprovider, a streamer and a major
OL,18,Fbroadband supplier, owned by the US
OL,19,Fgiant Comcast - with a takeover bid.
