OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FA price of #1.6 billion has been
OL,7,Fprovisionally agreed, so discussions
OL,8,Fhave clearly been going on for several
OL,9,Fmonths, but it is not a done deal yet.
OL,10,FThe due diligence continues.
OL,12,FSky and ITV have similar problems.
OL,13,FBoth are losing viewers to Netflix,
OL,14,FYouTube, Amazon, Apple and Disney+.
OL,16,FViewing habits have changed
OL,17,Fdramatically in a short space of time.
