OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FPre-Covid, six million people in the
OL,7,FUK would routinely sit down to watch
OL,8,FCoronation Street on a weekday
OL,9,Fevening. Today, ITV is pleased if four
OL,10,Fmillion tune in.
OL,12,FPublic service broadcasters in the UK
OL,13,Fare up against it. At the BBC, Channel
OL,14,F4 and Channel 5, audience numbers have
OL,15,Falso dropped sharply.
