OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FWe do not yet know what Sky would do
OL,7,Fwith the ITV brand, the channels, the
OL,8,FITVX app or the news service (ITV
OL,9,FStudios is not part of the bid), but
OL,10,Fif a final agreement is reached, the
OL,11,Fdeal would make Sky the biggest
OL,12,Fcommercial broadcaster in the UK - and
OL,13,Fby a country mile.
OL,15,FITV's free-to-air network would give
OL,16,FSky access to mass audiences, a bigger
OL,17,Fplatform to cross-promote Sky content,
OL,18,Fand the ability to reach and target
OL,19,Fviewers in a way that would appeal to
OL,20,Fadvertisers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
