OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,F"This is a consolidation and I think
OL,7,Fit's timely," says Peter Bazalgette, a
OL,8,Fformer chair of ITV, who supports the
OL,9,Ftakeover.
OL,11,FIndeed, he worries about the future of
OL,12,Fpublic service broadcasting if
OL,13,Fconsolidation does not happen.
OL,15,FIn his view, the competition is so
OL,16,Fintense that the UK market can only
OL,17,Fsupport two domestic broadcasters.
