OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,F"Think about our own viewing habits,"
OL,7,Fsays Bazalgette. "How often do we
OL,8,Fwatch the public service broadcasters?
OL,9,FBut they matter; they deliver
OL,10,Fincredibly important public service
OL,11,Fnews. We need that in the mad world of
OL,12,Fthe internet and the AI world we are
OL,13,Fin now."
OL,15,FSky will be hoping a takeover can
OL,16,Fdeliver savings too.
