OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,F"Sky News has to be a question mark,"
OL,7,Fsays Bazalgette. "It costs (Sky)
OL,8,Fupward of #100 million a year to do.
OL,9,FIt's a great news service and I don't
OL,10,Fknow, but all I'm saying is if they
OL,11,Fare looking for savings, they are only
OL,12,Flegally obliged to provide it for
OL,13,Fanother few years."
OL,15,FThere are hurdles ahead.
OL,17,FITV has commitments under the terms of
OL,18,Fits licence, which runs until 2034, to
OL,19,Fprovide national news at peak time,
OL,20,Fregional news, and to produce a
OL,21,Fcertain number of programmes in the UK.
