OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FSky would have to honour them. A Sky
OL,7,Ftakeover would also need regulatory
OL,8,Fapproval. Ofcom and the Competition
OL,9,Fand Markets Authority would want
OL,10,Freassurance that by joining forces,
OL,11,FSky and ITV do not become too dominant
OL,12,F- and that the quality of output would
OL,13,Fbe maintained.
OL,15,FThe Secretary of State, Lisa Nandy,
OL,16,Fwould also have to give her approval.
OL,18,FIn one sense, we have been here before.
