OL,3,CThe future of ITV: Sky and Comcast
OL,4,Cmake a #1.6 billion play
OL,6,FAlmost 20 years ago, Sky - then known
OL,7,Fas BSkyB - bought a 17.9% stake in ITV
OL,8,Fto block a takeover by NTL (which went
OL,9,Fon to become Virgin Media).
OL,11,FRegulators intervened and forced Sky
OL,12,Fto sell much of its shareholding at a
OL,13,Floss over competition concerns.
OL,15,FThe broadcasting world back then looks
OL,16,Falmost unrecognisable today.
